      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This specimen delivers linear power delivery through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, with a documented subframe reinforcement and recent replacement of the rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs). The suspension maintains factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. While showing minor stone peppering on the front fascia, the mechanical vitals are superb, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a smooth VANOS engagement. A mechanically sound, high-revving icon ready for the B-roads.",
